Pre-Game Insights: Madagascar and Gambia have failed to win any of their last 12 AFCON qualifying matches since November 2019.
Both sides are evenly matched on paper and we predict that they will cancel out each other's efforts at the Stade Larbi Zaouli.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Madagascar have called up 27 players for October's qualifying double-header against Gambia.
Gambia have named 23 players for their upcoming qualifying games, including Ablie Jallow, Omar Colley, and Yankuba Minteh.
